data.description: Beautifully updated and turn key! This ranch home has so much going for it! The home has a large lot with a wooded back yard view and a spacious grassy area. The patio hot tub is a definite bonus! Large living room open to the DR next to a large open kitchen with tiled floors and plenty of counter space. All the bathrooms have been beautifully updated and the upper floor has hardwood throughout. The over 1800 sq. ft. fully finished lower level offers a large gathering room, second kitchen, high top pass through bar area and a walk out basement. Large laundry room and two additional rooms finish off this entertaining space! So much to offer just a few minutes to OH, KY or downtown Huntington.
